{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"be20cdb256","title":"对《评陶铸的两本书》一文的几段批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ebf32bea48","index":0,"year":1967,"month":8,"day":20,"articleId":"be20cdb256","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"大批判","id":"07ed767d50","type":"主题"},{"name":"重要党内斗争和案件","id":"83b1479e48","type":"主题"},{"name":"批示","id":"9bc2c334c7","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"陶铸","id":"dbcf15bd08","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"e2305b9e63","type":"主题"},{"name":"中央文革","id":"ef71f03227","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"340ccccbf6","type":"title","text":"对《评陶铸的两本书》一文的几段批语","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"be20cdb256","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8dd80301a0","type":"paragraph","text":"文元同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"be20cdb256","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2918a6d6eb","type":"paragraph","text":"看了一遍，很好。题目似可改为《评陶铸的两本书》，小题目不要。此外，有些地方似太简略，宜于加以发挥。但文章已不短，再加或显得太长。究应如何，可与你的写作班子同志们一商，他们可能提出些好的意见。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"be20cdb256","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1e2a57609d","type":"paragraph","text":"看过，极好。我只改了几个字，加了一段话，是否妥当，请酌定。建议在北京发表，前一天广播，以便同北京在同一天在全国各报发表。还要先送北京，在中央文革，中央碰头会，以三四天时间加以讨论。如有好的意见，加以吸收。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"be20cdb256","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"44779bdbf2","type":"paragraph","text":"还宜在二三个月写几篇批刘文章，你是否有时间担负起来。明后日拟和你一谈。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"be20cdb256","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}